[normal]&#xa0; 
[normal]      
[normal]We must i[bold]mprove understanding &amp; awareness of young people &amp; parents[bold] with regard to opportunities and pathways towards them[bold]; even where appropriate services exist, people do not always know how to access them[bold].[bold]&#xa0;
